  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab your sticks, drum up the beat and unleash your inner Taiko Master!                          </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/7043d756ca562c9f7f30e2ec799bf7e8.poster.avif?t=1764772285\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/7043d756ca562c9f7f30e2ec799bf7e8.webm?t=1764772285\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/7043d756ca562c9f7f30e2ec799bf7e8.mp4?t=1764772285\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DRUM UP THE BEAT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Taiko Frenzy is a percussion rhythm game set in a stunning, colorful scenery. Immerse yourself in fantasy world inspired by Japanese folklore with original soundtracks exclusively composed for the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control the strength of your strikes to succeed in the accented beats and perfect your timing to the beat to unleash breathtaking sakura storms, boosting your score and creating a mesmerizing visual spectacle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/283b99b908a7c37b57a4740125ec05a5.poster.avif?t=1764772285\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/283b99b908a7c37b57a4740125ec05a5.webm?t=1764772285\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/283b99b908a7c37b57a4740125ec05a5.mp4?t=1764772285\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PROGRESS AT YOUR OWN PACE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each original track offers 4 difficulty levels providing a rewarding learning curve, easy to learn, hard to master! Customize the challenge with various game modifiers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb the leaderboards and strive to unlock all the medals, aiming to become the ultimate Taiko Master.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/67513e1ba77f322931ba1902795c4edc.poster.avif?t=1764772285\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/67513e1ba77f322931ba1902795c4edc.webm?t=1764772285\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/67513e1ba77f322931ba1902795c4edc.mp4?t=1764772285\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNLOCK LEGENDARY SKINS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your progress in songs is rewarded with XP and achievements, unlocking over 100 cosmetics. Satisfy your collector’s soul and showcase your unique style!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/724855854671a579ba2a6196254daebe.poster.avif?t=1764772285\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/724855854671a579ba2a6196254daebe.webm?t=1764772285\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/724855854671a579ba2a6196254daebe.mp4?t=1764772285\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE COMMUNITY SONGS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover and play songs created by players worldwide with the in-game Community Songs browser!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CREATE YOUR OWN SONGS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let your creativity flow with the custom song feature and creation tool, enabling you to compose and play your personalized drumming masterpieces, putting your creativity in the spotlight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/9bf1ab231d31be61e9a9956d240cd1cc.poster.avif?t=1764772285\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/9bf1ab231d31be61e9a9956d240cd1cc.webm?t=1764772285\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/9bf1ab231d31be61e9a9956d240cd1cc.mp4?t=1764772285\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to take on the challenge? Download Taiko Frenzy now and drum your way to mastery!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab your sticks, drum up the beat and unleash your inner Taiko Master!                          </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/7043d756ca562c9f7f30e2ec799bf7e8.poster.avif?t=1764772285\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/7043d756ca562c9f7f30e2ec799bf7e8.webm?t=1764772285\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/7043d756ca562c9f7f30e2ec799bf7e8.mp4?t=1764772285\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DRUM UP THE BEAT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Taiko Frenzy is a percussion rhythm game set in a stunning, colorful scenery. Immerse yourself in fantasy world inspired by Japanese folklore with original soundtracks exclusively composed for the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control the strength of your strikes to succeed in the accented beats and perfect your timing to the beat to unleash breathtaking sakura storms, boosting your score and creating a mesmerizing visual spectacle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/283b99b908a7c37b57a4740125ec05a5.poster.avif?t=1764772285\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/283b99b908a7c37b57a4740125ec05a5.webm?t=1764772285\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/283b99b908a7c37b57a4740125ec05a5.mp4?t=1764772285\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PROGRESS AT YOUR OWN PACE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each original track offers 4 difficulty levels providing a rewarding learning curve, easy to learn, hard to master! Customize the challenge with various game modifiers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb the leaderboards and strive to unlock all the medals, aiming to become the ultimate Taiko Master.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/67513e1ba77f322931ba1902795c4edc.poster.avif?t=1764772285\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/67513e1ba77f322931ba1902795c4edc.webm?t=1764772285\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/67513e1ba77f322931ba1902795c4edc.mp4?t=1764772285\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNLOCK LEGENDARY SKINS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your progress in songs is rewarded with XP and achievements, unlocking over 100 cosmetics. Satisfy your collector’s soul and showcase your unique style!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/724855854671a579ba2a6196254daebe.poster.avif?t=1764772285\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/724855854671a579ba2a6196254daebe.webm?t=1764772285\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/724855854671a579ba2a6196254daebe.mp4?t=1764772285\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE COMMUNITY SONGS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover and play songs created by players worldwide with the in-game Community Songs browser!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CREATE YOUR OWN SONGS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let your creativity flow with the custom song feature and creation tool, enabling you to compose and play your personalized drumming masterpieces, putting your creativity in the spotlight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/9bf1ab231d31be61e9a9956d240cd1cc.poster.avif?t=1764772285\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/9bf1ab231d31be61e9a9956d240cd1cc.webm?t=1764772285\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2680410/extras/9bf1ab231d31be61e9a9956d240cd1cc.mp4?t=1764772285\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to take on the challenge? Download Taiko Frenzy now and drum your way to mastery!</p>",
